\end{align*}
$$


<p>

And here is a system of equations with labels in an align environment:
$$
\begin{align}
a &= q + 4 + 5+ 6 \label{eq1} \\ 
b &= \nabla^2 u + \nabla^4 x \label{eq2}
\end{align}
$$

We can refer to \eqref{eq1}-\eqref{eq2}.

<p>
